# Admin / salesman SPA (Vite) — local dev
# Required: base URL of the FastAPI backend (no trailing slash).
VITE_API_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000

# Optional: force the sales (PIN-login) surface on localhost without DNS.
# Leave blank for the admin app; set to "sales" to exercise the salesman portal.
# VITE_FORCE_SUBDOMAIN=sales
